title: INGLOT Halal Breathable Nail Enamel O2M 535 Soft Matte Black
description: 11 ml/0.37 US FL OZ O2M Breathable Nail Enamel SOFT MATTE is a new formula of air and water permeable nail enamel. Provides perfect coverage and a subtle matte finish. The new flat brush was carefully picked for this formula to provide quick, easy and even coverage. Use with O2M Breathable Base to prolong life and improve application of the nail enamel. To achieve a classic glossy look, cover with a layer of O2M Breathable Top Coat. Both products also ensure air and water permeability. Does NOT contain toluene, formaldehyde, dibutyl phthalate (DBP) or camphor.
